## Risks (“furos”) — internal reminders

| Area | Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------|------------|
| **Node** | Biggest dropout for PMs; terminal fails early | **Apoio 1** video; instructor verifies Node before record |
| **`.cursorrules`** | Added too late | Create **before** first codegen chat |
| **`gerar-tasks`** | Model skips OK and dumps subtasks | Reinforce protocol from `gerar-tasks.md`; pause and ask user to confirm gate |
| **Terminal** | PM audience friction | Slow down for `npm run dev`; short explanations |
| **Supabase** | Live account creation kills pace | Pre-configure (**Apoio 2**); dry-run migration before record |
| **Migration errors** | Awkward on camera | **Do not panic**—use **Ask** or **change model** (**Princípio 7**: troca de modelo ao emperrar); pedagogically valuable |
| **Vercel** | OAuth / Authorize Cursor breaks flow | Logged in before recording |
| **Vercel build** | `createClient` crashes without env vars during static generation | **Fixed:** lazy `getSupabase()` defers init to runtime; build verified passing with empty env |
| **GitHub remote** | Stale origin pointing to deleted repo | Must create new repo before push; use `gh repo create` |
| **Recharts** | Empty chart | Data from **Supabase**, not LocalStorage; seed data first |
| **Git** | Commit fails | `user.name` / `user.email` set |

